document_data.name: Tammess Eldrake
document_data.mainbody: '''Tammess Eldrake''' was a member of the [[Council of Tarmalune|Council]] of [[Tarmalune]] as of [[1479 DR]].
document_data.Activities: As of 1479 DR, Tammess was dedicated to helping the poor citizens of Tarmalune, as well the honest workers of the city. However, she was one of the major criticizers of the [[Firequench Order]].
document_data.Relationships: Tammess was the onetime lover of [[Rathgar Malynd]], who tried to kill her at least three times after they parted.
